### Get all students
GET http://localhost:5000/api/students

### Add a new student
POST http://localhost:5000/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice",
  "grade": "A",
  "course": "Math"
}

### Update student
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/students/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice Updated",
  "grade": "A+",
  "course": "Math"
}

### Delete student
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/students/1

### Upload CSV
POST http://localhost:5000/api/students/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

# You need to attach a file here using REST Client's file feature